§. 2. Smaragdus on 1 Pet. 2. in oct. Paſch. fol. 87. ſaith, [Sinite parvulos venire ad me, talium enim eſt regnum coelorum: Hanc enim ſanctam, puram & innocentem infantiam, per baptiſmi gratiam caſta mater gignit Eccleſia] That is [ſuffer little children to come to me, for of ſuch is the Kingdom of God;
For this holy


pure and innocent Infancie, the Church their chaſt Mother doth by the grace of Baptiſm beget.]
